1422
00:49:35,266 --> 00:49:36,768
HAMIN: It's been ages since I did this.

1423
00:49:37,788 --> 00:49:39,936
(Even the youngest born in '08 are familiar)

1424
00:49:40,766 --> 00:49:46,400
