1556
00:54:36,096 --> 00:54:37,344
SONGHA: There might be points for creativity.

1557
00:54:37,664 --> 00:54:39,433
SONGHA: For example, it's kind of like this.

1558
00:54:39,466 --> 00:54:40,288
