HAMIN: Exactly at seven...

2062
01:09:56,160 --> 01:09:56,640
HARUTA: No, no.

2063
01:09:56,640 --> 01:09:57,792
CHARLIE: Yo!

2064
01:09:58,048 --> 01:09:58,700
CHARLIE: Yo!

2065
01:09:58,700 --> 01:09:59,488
(Run away)

2066
01:10:01,536 --> 01:10:01,952
JAEWON: Who is it?

2067
01:10:01,952 --> 01:10:03,566
DANIEL: Ah, why are they really doing this?

2068
01:10:04,433 --> 01:10:06,833
(Going for a home visit)

2069
01:10:06,833 --> 01:10:07,424
DANIEL: Hey, hey.

2070
01:10:08,704 --> 01:10:09,824
DANIEL: Hey.

2071
01:10:09,920 --> 01:10:11,840
JAEWON: What's the plan, can you memorize it?

2072
01:10:11,840 --> 01:10:12,766
CHARLIE: Exactly.

2073
01:10:12,766 --> 01:10:13,633
(Upset)
WOOLIN: Let's try it, let's do it first.

2074
01:10:13,633 --> 01:10:14,800
(Give it a try)
DANIEL: Go ahead, try.

2075
01:10:14,976 --> 01:10:15,296
HYUNJUN: One...

2076
01:10:15,296 --> 01:10:16,960
WOOLIN: One, two, three.

2077
01:10:16,960 --> 01:10:17,664
WOOLIN: Four, isn't it like this?

2078
01:10:17,664 --> 01:10:18,912
JAEWON: See, you can't memorize it.

2079
01:10:18,912 --> 01:10:19,552
TRAINEE: Was it like that?

2080
01:10:19,552 --> 01:10:20,448
(You know, these two are rivals)
JAEWON: He doesn't know, he doesn't know.

2081
01:10:20,704 --> 01:10:21,312
DANIEL: Let's go, let's go.

2082
01:10:21,312 --> 01:10:22,500
(Leave with relief)

2083
01:10:23,233 --> 01:10:25,466
(Thorough until the end)

2084
01:10:25,536 --> 01:10:26,240
WOOLIN: Let's go, let's go!

2085
01:10:26,400 --> 01:10:28,500
(Thought they left, but...)

2086
01:10:28,864 --> 01:10:29,632
(Class '00 actively practicing in the auditorium)
TRAINEE: Okay, okay.

2087
01:10:29,632 --> 01:10:30,720
SONGHA: We need to match, okay?

2088
01:10:30,720 --> 01:10:31,616
HANBI: Going in randomly...

2089
01:10:31,808 --> 01:10:34,300
(The auditorium door moves)
TRAINEE: Five, six, seven, eight.

2090
01:10:34,624 --> 01:10:35,840
HYUNJUN: Let's sneak a peek at just one idea.

2091
01:10:36,900 --> 01:10:37,792
(This time's spying target: Class '00)
HYUNJUN: Let's see what kind of vibe they're going for.

2092
01:10:37,792 --> 01:10:40,448
WOOLIN: Oh, but it's easy to get caught.
They're right in front.

2093
01:10:41,632 --> 01:10:43,968
(Peeking)
SONGHA: One, two, three, four.

2094
01:10:44,800 --> 01:10:47,033
HYUNJUN: They're lying down, completely lying down?

2095
01:10:48,000 --> 01:10:48,866
HYUNJUN: Lying all the way down!

2096
01:10:49,333 --> 01:10:51,133
HYUNJUN: Doing push-ups...

2097
01:10:51,133 --> 01:10:51,968
(For real)
WOOLIN: They're actually exercising.

2098
01:10:51,968 --> 01:10:53,024
- WOOLIN: Are they exercising?
- HYUNJUN: Can you see?

2099
01:10:53,344 --> 01:10:54,912
WOOLIN: I can't see anything at all.

2100
01:10:55,366 --> 01:10:57,100
(Limited view seats)

2101
01:10:57,533 --> 01:10:59,733
(Getting more daring)
WOOLIN: Do I need to put my whole head in to see?

2102
01:10:59,733 --> 01:11:02,366
WOOLIN: Ah, but looking at it... it's not fun at all.

2103
01:11:02,366 --> 01:11:02,912
HYUNJUN: What are they even doing?

2104
01:11:02,912 --> 01:11:03,424
WOOLIN: That's what I'm saying.

2105
01:11:03,424 --> 01:11:04,544
HYUNJUN: They're exercising.

2106
01:11:04,736 --> 01:11:05,024
TATA: Oh!

2107
01:11:05,632 --> 01:11:06,080
TATA: Oh!

2108
01:11:06,752 --> 01:11:07,488
(Scared)

2109
01:11:08,192 --> 01:11:09,312
(Scary)
WOOLIN: Oh, no.

2110
01:11:09,312 --> 01:11:11,488
(The big brother is angry)
HANBI: Oh, those '90s copycats.

2111
01:11:11,936 --> 01:11:13,333
HANBI: Oh, don't spy!

2112
01:11:13,952 --> 01:11:14,848
(Shaking)
WOOLIN: Let's run, let's run.

2113
01:11:15,533 --> 01:11:17,100
(Run away!)

2114
01:11:17,728 --> 01:11:18,880
(Fast footsteps)

2115
01:11:18,880 --> 01:11:20,666
(Leave in a cloud of dust)

2116
01:11:21,312 --> 01:11:23,552
(Two hours of evening practice passed)

2117
01:11:23,712 --> 01:11:24,256
SONGHA: What's next?

2118
01:11:24,704 --> 01:11:25,440
HANBI: Just a moment.

2119
01:11:25,440 --> 01:11:26,944
SONGHA: This is longer than I thought!

2120
01:11:26,944 --> 01:11:27,584
HANBI: Right.

2121
01:11:27,866 --> 01:11:29,120
(Putting together a gymnastics
routine is harder than it seems)

2122
01:11:29,120 --> 01:11:29,800
SONGHA: It's too long.

2123
01:11:29,800 --> 01:11:31,100
HANBI: Shouldn't we try testing

2124
01:11:31,100 --> 01:11:33,300
HANBI: whether we remember everything so far?

2125
01:11:33,568 --> 01:11:34,048
SONGHA: Should we try it just once?

2126
01:11:34,048 --> 01:11:34,833
HANBI: Let's try it just once.

2127
01:11:35,866 --> 01:11:37,833
(Trying it once up to where the choreography is done)

2128
01:11:44,300 --> 01:11:46,800
SONGHA: I'm going crazy because I can't remember.

2129
01:11:47,033 --> 01:11:48,833
(Wrong from the start)

2130
01:11:49,600 --> 01:11:52,166
(Compose yourself and go calmly again)

2131
01:11:54,200 --> 01:11:55,168
(Close call with the basics)

2132
01:11:55,264 --> 01:11:55,808
HANBI: Basics.

2133
01:11:57,100 --> 01:11:58,900
(Wrong moves)

2134
01:11:59,040 --> 01:11:59,488
SONGHA: What's next?

2135
01:12:00,133 --> 01:12:01,216
(Forgot the next move)
KACHIN: What's next?

2136
01:12:01,216 --> 01:12:01,952
SONGHA: What was it?

2137
01:12:02,144 --> 01:12:04,832
(Stamina already depleted)

2138
01:12:04,992 --> 01:12:05,920
SONGHA: It's really not ending.

2139
01:12:06,464 --> 01:12:07,296
(Need to plan neck exercises too)
SONGHA: Is the neck exercise next?

2140
01:12:07,296 --> 01:12:08,032
HANBI: Neck exercise.

2141
01:12:09,400 --> 01:12:10,336
HANBI: Do you have a good idea?

2142
01:12:11,008 --> 01:12:11,680
(Sigh)
KACHIN: Oh...

2143
01:12:12,256 --> 01:12:13,792
(Silent)

2144
01:12:13,952 --> 01:12:14,688
SONGHA: What do you want to do?

2145
01:12:15,168 --> 01:12:16,384
TATA: I don't know.

2146
01:12:16,384 --> 01:12:16,864
HANBI: This time...

2147
01:12:16,992 --> 01:12:17,824
HANBI: My brain isn't working.

2148
01:12:18,656 --> 01:12:19,808
(Overcoming all challenges)
HANBI: It's hard.

2149
01:12:19,808 --> 01:12:20,992
(Will they be able to finish the gymnastics routine?)
HANBI: Out of ideas.

2150
01:12:21,792 --> 01:12:24,533
(Class '10 resting after exhausting practice)

2151
01:12:24,864 --> 01:12:25,952
(Inhale)

2152
01:12:26,464 --> 01:12:27,840
(Exhale)

2153
01:12:28,133 --> 01:12:30,966
(They were supposed to start at 8)

2154
01:12:31,200 --> 01:12:33,433
(HARUTA)
(It's already past 9, you guys!)

2155
01:12:33,568 --> 01:12:35,840
(DANIEL)

2156
01:12:36,768 --> 01:12:37,376
HARUTA: When are we starting?

2157
01:12:39,776 --> 01:12:41,166
DANIEL: We have to do it.

2158
01:12:41,600 --> 01:12:42,733
DANIEL: Did the others finish?

2159
01:12:43,066 --> 01:12:43,904
(Still half-asleep, checking on other classes)
HARUTA: What?

2160
01:12:43,904 --> 01:12:45,152
DANIEL: Did the others finish?

2161
01:12:46,800 --> 01:12:50,033
(Meanwhile, Class '00 is finished with practice)

2162
01:12:50,433 --> 01:12:51,800
DANIEL: First, everyone needs to get up.

2163
01:12:51,800 --> 01:12:52,480
(HAMIN's sleeping,
JAEWON's sleeping)

2164
01:12:52,480 --> 01:12:53,440
CHARLIE: Okay.

2165
01:12:53,440 --> 01:12:54,112
HARUTA: Wake up!

2166
01:12:54,528 --> 01:12:56,160
(Self rooster alarm)
CHARLIE: Cock-a-doodle-doo!

2167
01:12:58,833 --> 01:13:00,900
(Back to the practice room after an hour)
CHARLIE: It's not even 10 yet!

2168
01:13:01,088 --> 01:13:03,533
DANIEL: Oh, wait, this isn't right...

2169
01:13:04,512 --> 01:13:05,856
(Back to resting)

2170
01:13:06,560 --> 01:13:07,776
DANIEL: Let's rest until the 40-minute mark.

2171
01:13:08,640 --> 01:13:09,696
DANIEL: HARUTA hasn't come yet.

2172
01:13:10,016 --> 01:13:12,416
(Were you looking for me?)

2173
01:13:13,066 --> 01:13:13,888
(Resuming practice)

2174
01:13:13,888 --> 01:13:16,352
DANIEL: First, let's decide what to do with 'Ba-am'.

2175
01:13:16,533 --> 01:13:21,568
DANIEL: Let's express the emotions
we feel from the song through our bodies.

2176
01:13:21,568 --> 01:13:22,240
CHARLIE: Okay, okay.

2177
01:13:22,933 --> 01:13:24,600
(Starting the expression)

2178
01:13:24,866 --> 01:13:25,856
(Three people are expressing)

2179
01:13:25,856 --> 01:13:26,624
CHARLIE: What?

2180
01:13:27,000 --> 01:13:29,766
(Blank stares)

2181
01:13:29,952 --> 01:13:30,752
DANIEL: You try it.

2182
01:13:34,496 --> 01:13:36,544
HARUTA: Ah... This is when you should do it.

2183
01:13:36,736 --> 01:13:37,344
HARUTA: When we're not filming...

2184
01:13:37,504 --> 01:13:39,424
(Noisy CHARLIE)
HARUTA: you were doing it like this.

2185
01:13:39,616 --> 01:13:40,224
HARUTA: But right now...

2186
01:13:40,224 --> 01:13:41,184
(Calm CHARLIE)

2187
01:13:41,184 --> 01:13:43,296
HARUTA: What? Hurry up and do it.

2188
01:13:43,733 --> 01:13:46,200
(Drinking a bowl of digestive aid)

2189
01:13:46,200 --> 01:13:47,072
DANIEL: I want to do this part at the front...

2190
01:13:47,072 --> 01:13:48,633
CHARLIE: Let's do it, let's do it.

2191
01:13:48,633 --> 01:13:49,280
(*Noisy CHARLIE returns)

2192
01:13:49,280 --> 01:13:49,824
CHARLIE: Are you saying we should?

2193
01:13:49,824 --> 01:13:50,624
DANIEL: Let's do it.

2194
01:13:50,624 --> 01:13:51,360
HARUTA: Please.

2195
01:13:51,520 --> 01:13:53,056
HARUTA: CHARLIE, CHARLIE...

2196
01:13:53,056 --> 01:13:56,900
HARUTA: Stand up now.

2197
01:13:56,900 --> 01:14:01,033
(Repeat playback)
HARUTA: Stand up now.

2198
01:14:01,233 --> 01:14:04,633
(Why are you doing this at night?)
HARUTA: Stand up now.

2199
01:14:04,704 --> 01:14:05,696
(Have a headache)

2200
01:14:05,696 --> 01:14:06,016
HARUTA: Stand up quickly.

2201
01:14:06,016 --> 01:14:08,864
(Stunned... CHARLIE joins)

2202
01:14:09,500 --> 01:14:11,333
(JAEWON also joins)

2203
01:14:11,333 --> 01:14:14,560
(Turns away)

2204
01:14:17,466 --> 01:14:23,800
(For 10 minutes, the round song continued)

2205
01:14:24,256 --> 01:14:25,800
(Due to the noise through the wall, Class '90 visits)
TRAINEE: What are you doing?

2206
01:14:25,800 --> 01:14:27,456
HARUTA: Stand up now.

2207
01:14:27,456 --> 01:14:29,088
- DANIEL: Oh, really noisy.
- HARUTA: Stand up now.

2208
01:14:29,088 --> 01:14:31,168
DANIEL: They're noisier than you, HYUNJUN.

2209
01:14:33,033 --> 01:14:35,233
(Adding more noisy person)

2210
01:14:36,833 --> 01:14:39,833
(Noisy No. 1 pushing back Noisy No. 2)

2211
01:14:41,312 --> 01:14:43,566
(More additions)

2212
01:14:43,833 --> 01:14:44,736
(Chaos)

2213
01:14:44,736 --> 01:14:46,368
HARUTA: They're smitten.

2214
01:14:46,848 --> 01:14:50,266
(One thing they've overlooked)
HARUTA: They're smitten.

2215
01:14:50,533 --> 01:14:52,966
(There are people downstairs)

2216
01:14:53,280 --> 01:14:55,072
(Rumble)

2217
01:14:55,400 --> 01:14:58,666
(Who made the noise?)

2218
01:15:01,216 --> 01:15:02,240
SONGHA: Ugh, it's noisy.

2219
01:15:03,700 --> 01:15:08,033
(Quietly went up to the practice room)

2220
01:15:08,400 --> 01:15:10,900
(Stop)

2221
01:15:11,300 --> 01:15:14,500
(The noise reaches its peak)
TRAINEES: Stand up now.

2222
01:15:15,200 --> 01:15:17,536
(Sneakily)

2223
01:15:17,536 --> 01:15:20,900
TRAINEES: Stand up now.

2224
01:15:20,900 --> 01:15:23,533
(Finally, the door opened)

2225
01:15:24,000 --> 01:15:25,984
(SONGHA has been spotted)

2226
01:15:29,440 --> 01:15:30,336
HYUNJUN: Stand up now!

2227
01:15:30,600 --> 01:15:32,933
(Ear attack)

2228
01:15:34,528 --> 01:15:36,224
SONGHA: The noise between floors...

2229
01:15:36,224 --> 01:15:37,216
TRAINEE: My ears are exploding.

2230
01:15:37,216 --> 01:15:38,848
SONGHA: I thought my ears were going to fall off.

2231
01:15:38,848 --> 01:15:39,616
CHARLIE: Wow.

2232
01:15:39,616 --> 01:15:40,960
HYUNJUN: Hey, isn't this being filmed?

2233
01:15:41,056 --> 01:15:41,824
CHARLIE: Yeah.

2234
01:15:41,824 --> 01:15:43,104
SONGHA: It's already been filmed.

2235
01:15:43,104 --> 01:15:44,500
SONGHA: How many cameras are there already?

2236
01:15:44,500 --> 01:15:46,033
(So many)
SONGHA: Please count them.

2237
01:15:46,266 --> 01:15:47,808
(Impossible not to be captured here)
SONGHA: I wondered why it's not filmed.

2238
01:15:47,808 --> 01:15:49,696
SONGHA: They're all around 360 degrees.

2239
01:15:49,696 --> 01:15:50,624
DANIEL: Over there, here.

2240
01:15:50,976 --> 01:15:52,512
DANIEL: There are eight cameras here.

2241
01:15:52,608 --> 01:15:54,240
CHARLIE: Now I feel embarrassed.

2242
01:15:54,666 --> 01:15:56,900
(Class '90 goes back to practice)
TRAINEE: Speak up a bit.

2243
01:15:56,900 --> 01:15:57,856
DANIEL: SONGHA, please leave now.

2244
01:15:57,952 --> 01:15:58,752
SONGHA: Do I have to go out?

2245
01:16:00,066 --> 01:16:02,100
(Seeing SONGHA off)

2246
01:16:02,866 --> 01:16:04,566
(About to start practice again)
CHARLIE: Let's hurry.

2247
01:16:04,566 --> 01:16:06,400
DANIEL: Ah, where did he go again...

2248
01:16:06,400 --> 01:16:10,900
(Can they complete it?)
CHARLIE: JAEWON, stand up now.

2249
01:16:10,900 --> 01:16:12,416
(Current time: 10:30)

2250
01:16:12,416 --> 01:16:13,664
CHARLIE: Just one more time and...

2251
01:16:13,664 --> 01:16:15,040
HARUTA: I can't do it today!

2252
01:16:15,466 --> 01:16:16,032
(Students have exhausted all their energy...)

2253
01:16:16,032 --> 01:16:17,536
(No wonder...)

2254
01:16:17,888 --> 01:16:19,584
JUSTIN: Quickly, go to sleep, everyone.

2255
01:16:19,840 --> 01:16:20,512
JUSTIN: Good night.

2256
01:16:20,512 --> 01:16:23,552
(What will happen
to the Idol Gymnastics Routine Presentation?)

2257
01:16:23,872 --> 01:16:25,024
(After the noisy night passed...)

2258
01:16:25,024 --> 01:16:30,464
(It's the fourth day of
Idol Gymnastics Routine Presentation)

2259
01:16:30,966 --> 01:16:35,166
(Between practice and play,
the tired members are fast asleep...)

2260
01:16:37,504 --> 01:16:38,880
(Surprised)

2261
01:16:39,933 --> 01:16:42,300
(Even after falling out of bed, still fast asleep)

2262
01:16:43,066 --> 01:16:45,233
(CHARLIE is having a sound sleep with TORONG)

2263
01:16:46,100 --> 01:16:49,000
(TORONG is like a bamboo wife)

2264
01:16:49,066 --> 01:16:52,133
(But KACHIN's bed is empty?)

2265
01:16:52,133 --> 01:16:55,933
(Not really, KACHIN is under the blanket)

2266
01:16:56,500 --> 01:16:59,333
(At that time, the next room wakes to the alarm)

2267
01:16:59,733 --> 01:17:02,400
(Throwing off the rabbit sleep mask)

2268
01:17:02,400 --> 01:17:05,766
(Still dazed from sleep)

2269
01:17:05,766 --> 01:17:09,866
(Folding the blanket as he wakes up)

2270
01:17:10,166 --> 01:17:12,166
(Meanwhile, TATA also wakes up)

2271
01:17:12,288 --> 01:17:15,776
(TATA gets dressed up as soon as he wakes up)

2272
01:17:16,064 --> 01:17:16,960
KASSHO: I'm awake.

2273
01:17:16,960 --> 01:17:18,633
(WOOLIN tries to wake up KASSHO from the same class)

2274
01:17:18,848 --> 01:17:20,333
WOOLIN: Wake up, man.

2275
01:17:20,333 --> 01:17:22,112
(Today is the presentation day, feeling rushed)

2276
01:17:22,112 --> 01:17:23,360
WOOLIN: It's past wake-up time.

2277
01:17:23,552 --> 01:17:24,288
KASSHO: Really?

2278
01:17:24,288 --> 01:17:24,768
WOOLIN: Yeah.

2279
01:17:25,400 --> 01:17:27,700
(Lounge)
(Meanwhile, in the lounge)

2280
01:17:27,808 --> 01:17:28,608
(Three friends are doing skincare)
NICHOLAS: I'll apply it for you.

2281
01:17:28,928 --> 01:17:29,440
HYUNJUN: Put it on for me.

2282
01:17:34,600 --> 01:17:35,733
HYUNJUN: Oh!

2283
01:17:36,200 --> 01:17:38,304
(HYUNJUN's face is being cared for on each side)
JUSTIN: Is that how you should apply it?

2284
01:17:38,592 --> 01:17:41,472
HYUNJUN: But this fits along the face line like this.

2285
01:17:42,366 --> 01:17:42,976
HYUNJUN: It's moist.

2286
01:17:42,976 --> 01:17:43,680
JUSTIN: Yeah, oh.

2287
01:17:44,064 --> 01:17:45,984
HYUNJUN: This is big and fits perfectly on the face.

2288
01:17:46,144 --> 01:17:46,624
HYUNJUN: Try it.

2289
01:17:46,624 --> 01:17:48,533
JUSTIN: I should put it on too.

2290
01:17:48,768 --> 01:17:50,033
JUSTIN: This feels cool.

2291
01:17:50,800 --> 01:17:51,933
NICHOLAS: It's really cool.

2292
01:17:52,096 --> 01:17:53,696
NICHOLAS: It would be really good
before putting on makeup.

2293
01:17:53,952 --> 01:17:55,200
HYUNJUN: It's good even before bed.

2294
01:17:55,200 --> 01:17:57,216
HYUNJUN: Even after applying for almost 20 minutes...

2295
01:17:57,472 --> 01:17:58,208
HYUNJUN: It's not dry.

2296
01:17:58,208 --> 01:17:59,104
JUSTIN: Was it moist?

2297
01:18:03,776 --> 01:18:04,533
HYUNJUN: Well.

2298
01:18:04,533 --> 01:18:05,900
HYUNJUN: Even when you squeeze, it keeps coming out.

2299
01:18:05,900 --> 01:18:07,360
